3. cs.LG - The paper discusses the use of ensemble approaches for adaptively changing network size, which is a common technique in machine learning and falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.SY - The paper mentions the implementation of the proposed method on a chip that includes an MSP430 microprocessor along with an on-chip switching mode DC-DC converter for dynamic voltage and frequency scaling, which falls under the domain of systems engineering. 
5. cs.NE - The paper proposes a method for reducing the computation energy of IoT systems using low precision computing and low complexity neural networks, which falls under the domain of neural engineering.
